name: JRV Art
body:
### Bio
My name is John Velickovic and I am a Studio Artist currently living and working in Southern California. I am a 4th year majoring in Studio Art and minoring in Digital Art and Management. Some of my skills include:

```
- Painting
- Photography
- Sculpture
- Design
```

Pintour blog- https://jrvart.wordpress.com/
